message.content: I'm really sorry to hear that you are feeling this way. Please know that there are people who care about you and resources available to help you through this difficult time. It's important to reach out to a mental health professional or a trusted friend or family member for support. You can also contact a crisis hotline or the emergency services in your area for immediate assistance. Your life is valuable and there is hope for a better tomorrow. Please take care and seek help.
